 <text>
  <front>
   <head>Verses sent to a Lady, who took Delight in ridiculing a Person of very weak Under-standing, whom she reliev'd from Want.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">you employ your Ridicule,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">On those who Pity claim?</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Think, , is the native Fool</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">For Wit a proper Theme?</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="2" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">On Vice your hum'rous Vein display;</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">'Tis meritorious there;</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Or tow'ring Vanity allay;</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">But, O! Misfortune spare.</l>
    </lg>
    <lg n="3" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">With Wisdom who endows the Brain,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">To thy Remembrance call;</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Nor, while the Wretched you sustain,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Tincture their Cup with Gall.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
